[Breeding for resistance to late blight disease is a major component in
disease management. Information on some aspects of the disease and breeding
for resistance can be found in the following web sites:
<http://www.cipotato.org/market/PgmRprts/pr95-96/contprog3.htm>
<http://www.cipotato.org/Projects/potato/lateblight/features.htm>
A short account of genetic engineering of potato for resistance to late
blight can be found in the following web site:
<http://sun.ars-grin.gov/hcrl/rrm-genetic.htm>. - Mod.DH
